Requirements

1) Its should be a Multiplayer Game
2) Customizable Board in terms of Snake and Ladder Placement and
Board Size
3) Customizable in terms of number of dice and
3) When game board loads it should
  a) Load the configured board size
  b) Load the configured snake and ladder
  c) Load the configured number of dice
